{"word":"H3474 - יָשַׁר - yâshar - yaw-shar' - Direct","slug":"H3474","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יָשַׁר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>yâshar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yaw-shar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Direct"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D9;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05E8; - ya&#x0302;shar</b> - <i>yaw-shar'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>be straight</i> or <i>even</i>; figuratively to <i>be</i> (causatively to <i>make</i>) <i>right</i>, <i>pleasant</i>, <i>prosperous: - </i>direct, fit, seem good (meet), + please (well), be (esteem, go) right (on), bring (look, make, take the) straight (way), be upright (-ly)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3475\">H3475</a>, <a href=\"#/H3476\">H3476</a>, <a href=\"#/H3477\">H3477</a>, <a href=\"#/H3483\">H3483</a>, <a href=\"#/H3484\">H3484</a>, <a href=\"#/H4334\">H4334</a>, <a href=\"#/H4339\">H4339</a>, <a href=\"#/H8289\">H8289</a>, <a href=\"#/H8290\">H8290</a>"}]}